com.microsoft.windowsazure.mobileservices

Interface ServiceFilter


  • public interface ServiceFilter
    The service filter can be used to manipulate requests and responses in the HTTP pipeline used by the MobileServiceClient. ServiceFilters can be associated with a MobileServiceClient via the WithFilter method.
